  title `Short title and commencement.`
  content obj_root_law_sections_1_content
  footnotes obj_root_law_sections_1_footnotes
  query abv=CEN&statehandle=123456789/1362&actid=AC_CEN_3_20_00075_193810_1535002780703&sectionId=29813&sectionno=1&orderno=1&orgactid=AC_CEN_3_20_00075_193810_1535002780703
obj_root_law_sections_1_content:
  string
  line `(1) This Act may be called the Cutchi Memons Act, 1938.`
  line
  line `(2) It shall come into force on the 1st day of November, 1938.`
obj_root_law_sections_1_footnotes:
  string
  line
obj_root_law_sections_2:
  sectionId (29814)
  sectionNo (2)
  orderNo 2
  title `Cutchi Memons to be governed in certain matters by Muhammadan Law.`
  content obj_root_law_sections_2_content
  footnotes obj_root_law_sections_2_footnotes
  query abv=CEN&statehandle=123456789/1362&actid=AC_CEN_3_20_00075_193810_1535002780703&sectionId=29814&sectionno=2&orderno=2&orgactid=AC_CEN_3_20_00075_193810_1535002780703
obj_root_law_sections_2_content:
  string
  line `Subject to the`
  line `provisions of section 3, all Cutchi Memons shall, in matters of succession and inheritance, be governed by`
  line `the Muhammadan Law.`
obj_root_law_sections_2_footnotes:
  string
  line
obj_root_law_sections_3:
  sectionId (29815)
  sectionNo (3)
  orderNo 3
  title Savings.
  content obj_root_law_sections_3_content
  footnotes obj_root_law_sections_3_footnotes
  query abv=CEN&statehandle=123456789/1362&actid=AC_CEN_3_20_00075_193810_1535002780703&sectionId=29815&sectionno=3&orderno=3&orgactid=AC_CEN_3_20_00075_193810_1535002780703
obj_root_law_sections_3_content:
  string
  line `Nothing in this Act shall affect any right or liability acquired or incurred before its`
  line `commencement, or any legal proceeding or remedy in respect of any such right or liability; and any such`
  line `legal proceeding or remedy may be continued or enforced as if this Act had not been passed.`
obj_root_law_sections_3_footnotes:
  string
  line
